Package com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.tier_0s.locale_services

Class LocaleServicesFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.tier_0s.locale_services.LocaleServicesFactory
  • public class LocaleServicesFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    LocaleServicesFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.tier_0s.locale_services package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
